\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula $f(k,q,t)=-\frac{e^{-i(\nu_{k}+\nu_{q})t}}{[i(\nu_{k}+\nu_{q}-\omega_{ac})-\frac{1}{2}\Gamma_{a}][i(\nu_{q}-\omega_{bc})-\frac{1}{2}\Gamma_{b}]}-\frac{e^{i(-\omega_{ac})t-\frac{\Gamma_{a}}{2}t}}{[i(\nu_{k}+\nu_{q}-\omega_{ac})-\frac{1}{2}\Gamma_{a}][i(\nu_{k}-\omega_{ab})-\frac{1}{2}(\Gamma_{a}-\Gamma_{b})]}+\frac{e^{i(-\nu_{k}-\omega_{bc})t-\frac{\Gamma_{b}}{2}t}}{[i(\nu_{k}-\omega_{ab})-\frac{1}{2}(\Gamma_{a}-\Gamma_{b})][i(\nu_{q}-\omega_{bc})-\frac{1}{2}\Gamma_{b}]}$
